---
import { getImage } from 'astro:assets'

import talentDesktop from '../../assets/about/desktop/image-world-class-talent.jpg'
import talentMobile from '../../assets/about/mobile/image-world-class-talent.jpg'
import talentTablet from '../../assets/about/tablet/image-world-class-talent.jpg'

const taletMobileOpt = await getImage({ src: talentMobile, format: 'avif' })
const talentTabletOpt = await getImage({ src: talentTablet, format: 'avif' })
const talentDesktopOpt = await getImage({ src: talentDesktop, format: 'avif' })
---

<section class="md:mt-[120px] lg:mt-[160px]">
  <div class="max-w-[1111px] mx-auto w-full md:px-10 xl:px-0 lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_635px]">
    <picture>
      <source
        media="(max-width: 767px)"
        srcset={taletMobileOpt.src}
        width={taletMobileOpt.attributes.width}
        height={taletMobileOpt.attributes.height}
      />
      <source
        media="(min-width: 1100px)"
        srcset={talentDesktopOpt.src}
        width={talentDesktopOpt.attributes.width}
        height={talentDesktopOpt.attributes.height}
      />
      <source
        media="(min-width: 768px)"
        srcset={talentTabletOpt.src}
        width={talentTabletOpt.attributes.width}
        height={talentTabletOpt.attributes.height}
      />
      <img
        src={talentDesktopOpt.src}
        alt=""
        width={talentDesktopOpt.attributes.width}
        height={talentDesktopOpt.attributes.height}
        class="w-full md:rounded-t-[15px] lg:rounded-r-none lg:rounded-l-[15px]"
      />
    </picture>
    <div
      class="h-[545px] md:h-[416px] lg:h-[640px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-white px-6 md:px-[58px] gap-6 bg-[#FDF3F0] md:rounded-b-[15px] lg:rounded-l-none lg:rounded-r-[15px] lg:items-start lg:pl-[95px]"
    >
      <h1
        class="font-medium text-peach text-[32px] leading-[36px] md:text-[40px] md:leading-[48px]"
      >
        World-class talent
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-black text-[15px] leading-[25px] text-center md:text-[16px] md:leading-[26px] lg:text-left lg:max-w-[458px]"
      >
        We are a crew of strategists, problem-solvers, and technologists. Every design is
        thoughtfully crafted from concept to launch, ensuring success in its given market. We are
        constantly updating our skills in a myriad of platforms.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-black text-[15px] leading-[25px] text-center md:text-[16px] md:leading-[26px] lg:text-left lg:max-w-[458px]"
      >
        Our team is multi-disciplinary and we are not merely interested in form — content and
        meaning are just as important. We give great importance to craftsmanship, service, and
        prompt delivery. Clients have always been impressed with our high-quality outcomes that
        encapsulates their brand’s story and mission.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
